{"tid":2445302,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【老牌豪宅】換樓客半億買香港花園4房戶 望維港海景+豪宅地段","createTime":"2021-03-13T13:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T09:07:51.000Z","uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"29eec081b2afb1094cfb9454d14098f0cf01dcef","tid":2445302,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:46:32.000Z","msg":"【老牌豪宅】換樓客半億買香港花園4房戶 望維港海景+豪宅地段<br />\n15:00 2021/03/13<br />\n<br />\n&quot;......西摩道8號香港花園，樓齡約46年，由於位處豪宅地段及提供大單位，故受到豪宅買家垂青，該行剛促成的為中層B室單位，實用面積約為1,991平方呎......為四房雙套間格，擁維港海景，而且單位更連2個車位。同區換樓客鍾情，加上看好後市，故斥近半億元，以4,938萬元意頭價承接，折合實用呎價約為24,802元......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2900565/%E3%80%90%E8%80%81%E7%89%8C%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85%E3%80%91%E6%8F%9B%E6%A8%93%E5%AE%A2%E5%8D%8A%E5%84%84%E8%B2%B7%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%8A%B1%E5%9C%924%E6%88%BF%E6%88%B6%20%20%E6%9C%9B%E7%B6%AD%E6%B8%AF%E6%B5%B7%E6%99%AF+%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85%E5%9C%B0%E6%AE%B5?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2900565%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%2580%2581%25E7%2589%258C%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%25AE%2585%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%258F%259B%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%2584%2584%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%259C%25924%25E6%2588%25BF%25E6%2588%25B6%2520%2520%25E6%259C%259B%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%2599%25AF%2B%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%25AE%2585%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%25AE%25B5%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfDcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=daf88227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2900565/%E3%80%90%E8%80%81%E7%89%8C%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85%E3%80%91%E6%8F%9B%E6%A8%93%E5%AE%A2%E5%8D%8A%E5%84%84%E8%B2%B7%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%8A%B1%E5%9C%924%E6%88%BF%E6%88%B6%20%20%E6%9C%9B%E7%B6%AD%E6%B8%AF%E6%B5%B7%E6%99%AF+%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85%E5%9C%B0%E6%AE%B5?mtc=60037</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">又一低水豪宅成交，位處半山及有海景，呎價都只是24.8k (因為包括2個車位，所以實質呎價其實更低)。</s